      "description": "## What's New\n\n- **Save button loading state:** Prevents double-clicks when saving a project — button shows \"Saving...\" and disables during save\n- **Cleaner project list:** Removed redundant \"Destination:\" prefix from project descriptions\n- **Auto-update paths on vault moves:** Route destination paths automatically update when you rename or move files/folders in your vault\n- **BRAT installation support:** Added BRAT install instructions to README for easier plugin installation and updates\n- **Refactored sync pipeline:** Priority job sync for faster deep-link opens — target file opens immediately while remaining jobs sync in the background",
