      "author": "iamjarins",
      "description": "[FlowState](https://findflow.ai/) is the missing bridge between offline notes and your digital brain. The plugin transcribes handwritten notes and voice memos using AI, and automatically stores the files exactly where you want in your Obsidian vault.\r\n\r\n  Features:\r\n  - AI-powered transcription of handwritten notes and audio\r\n  - Enrichment options (translate, summarize, extract action items, etc.)\r\n  - Multiple projects with custom destinations\r\n  - Create new files or append to existing ones\r\n  - Email to upload files\r\n  - Download original files to vault",
      "downloadCount": 7,
